00:16:29.850 --> 00:16:30.850
kay Minato...

00:16:34.260 --> 00:16:35.260
Nakalimutan ko na.

00:16:47.910 --> 00:16:49.480
Ito ba ang lugar?

00:16:51.860 --> 00:16:53.380
Wala akong maalala.

00:16:59.560 --> 00:17:00.560
Ay naku.

00:17:01.160 --> 00:17:02.660
Well, well, well.

00:17:03.020 --> 00:17:05.020
Oh, kung hindi ikaw, mister.

00:17:05.440 --> 00:17:06.740
Naaalala mo ba ako?

00:17:07.370 --> 00:17:08.370
Uh...

00:17:09.500 --> 00:17:11.510
Isa...

00:17:11.850 --> 00:17:13.650
Ikaw ay tulad ng sinabi ni Minato-chan na magiging ikaw.

00:17:13.810 --> 00:17:15.880
At pagkatapos mong ibuhos ang iyong puso sa akin.

00:17:17.230 --> 00:17:18.230
pasensya na po.

00:17:20.280 --> 00:17:21.280
Kaya?

00:17:21.960 --> 00:17:23.060
Ang iyong nasirang puso...

00:17:23.110 --> 00:17:24.280
gumaling na ba?

00:17:25.350 --> 00:17:26.350
Oo.

00:17:26.870 --> 00:17:28.540
Lahat ito ay salamat kay Minato.

00:17:28.870 --> 00:17:31.940
Oh, ganun ba? Iyan ay kahanga-hanga.

00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:36.720
- Um... sabi niya pupunta siya ngayon.
- Nandito siya.

00:17:37.250 --> 00:17:38.450
May plano ba kayong dalawa?

00:17:38.650 --> 00:17:39.650
Ay, hindi.

00:17:39.780 --> 00:17:41.000
May nakalimutan siya kaya dinala ko.

00:17:41.060 --> 00:17:43.130
Naku, napaka thoughtful mo.

00:17:43.860 --> 00:17:45.120
Palabas na ako.

00:17:45.210 --> 00:17:46.310
Naka-unlock ang pinto.

00:17:46.430 --> 00:17:47.630
Ipasok mo lang ang sarili mo.

00:17:48.550 --> 00:17:50.450
Okay, salamat.

00:17:50.480 --> 00:17:51.680
See you next time.

00:17:57.330 --> 00:17:59.670
To think sinabi niya, "It's all thanks to Minato."

00:18:00.340 --> 00:18:01.730
Iba ka, Minato-chan.

00:18:02.650 --> 00:18:05.560
Ang aking instinct ay hindi kailanman mali.

00:18:08.100 --> 00:18:11.890
- Sobrang cute.
- Mayroon akong isang ito.

00:18:13.090 --> 00:18:14.090
Sobrang cute.

00:18:14.150 --> 00:18:16.210
Mmm, ito ay masarap!

00:18:16.650 --> 00:18:18.030
Minato-chan namin yun.

00:18:18.090 --> 00:18:20.010
Siya ay may mahusay na panlasa sa mga souvenir.

00:18:20.180 --> 00:18:23.000
Mayaman yan galing sa
nagpasabog ng phone ko kaninang umaga.

00:18:23.000 --> 00:18:23.600
Hoy!

00:18:23.690 --> 00:18:24.890
May naaabala ba tayo?

00:18:26.990 --> 00:18:28.600
Ah, hindi naman niya itinatanggi.

00:18:30.270 --> 00:18:31.900
Sabi ko naman sayo, wala lang.

00:18:31.970 --> 00:18:34.090
Paanong wala?

00:18:34.290 --> 00:18:37.210
Nagpunta ka sa isang amusement park
at pagkatapos ay nagpalipas ka ng gabi.

00:18:37.700 --> 00:18:39.610
Jeez! Panatilihin ang iyong boses.

00:18:39.620 --> 00:18:40.690
Kaya ano ang eksaktong nangyari?

00:18:40.690 --> 00:18:42.830
- Sabihin na sa amin!
- Iwanan mo ako.

00:18:43.390 --> 00:18:44.390
Kumain ka na lang ng dessert mo.

00:18:44.450 --> 00:18:47.150
- Magpakita man lang sa amin ng larawan.
- Oo!

00:18:47.210 --> 00:18:51.130
- I told you, walang pictures.
- Hindi mo man lang kinunan ng litrato ang lalaking gusto mo?

00:18:51.330 --> 00:18:54.190
- Ilang photographer ka.
- Ano?

00:18:55.840 --> 00:18:56.840
Hoy, sandali.

00:18:57.400 --> 00:18:59.760
Nangangahulugan ba ito na nanalo si Minato-chan sa taya?

00:19:01.160 --> 00:19:02.160
Oh.

00:19:02.350 --> 00:19:03.350
Oo.

00:19:03.960 --> 00:19:05.280
Di ba nasabi ko na sa inyo?

00:19:05.640 --> 00:19:06.970
Wala akong pakialam kung gaano ka-straight ang isang lalaki.

00:19:07.170 --> 00:19:08.670
Kaya ko palagi...

00:19:08.750 --> 00:19:09.950
gawin mo siyang akin.

00:19:11.040 --> 00:19:14.030
Napakadaling tawagin itong taya.

00:19:14.360 --> 00:19:16.270
Ngunit isang deal ay isang deal.

00:19:16.560 --> 00:19:20.980
Hindi pwede. Sobra na ang pag-ahit ng ulo ko.

00:19:21.160 --> 00:19:22.910
Pero hey, Minato-chan...

00:19:23.480 --> 00:19:26.050
Sa palagay ko ay hindi magandang ideya ang paghihiganti.

00:19:26.360 --> 00:19:28.110
Dahil ang lalaking iyon...

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:29.400
may nararamdaman talaga siya sayo ngayon diba?

00:19:30.980 --> 00:19:33.180
Tungkol dun...

00:19:35.370 --> 00:19:37.280
Ang nararamdaman ko para kay Shizuma...

00:19:37.970 --> 00:19:39.680
Hindi ko na mararamdaman yun.

00:20:04.440 --> 00:20:05.540
Ito.

00:20:06.440 --> 00:20:07.540
Nakalimutan mo na ito.

00:20:08.510 --> 00:20:09.510
Ah.

00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:16.160
Shizuma.

00:20:20.560 --> 00:20:21.810
Teka, Shizuma.

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:27.150
Teka, teka lang.

00:20:27.390 --> 00:20:28.390
Hey.

00:20:33.310 --> 00:20:34.510
Lahat ba ay...

00:20:35.950 --> 00:20:37.320
Kasinungalingan ba ang lahat?

00:20:39.010 --> 00:20:40.010
Hindi, hindi iyon.

00:20:41.180 --> 00:20:42.180
Kailangan kong sabihin sa kanya.

00:20:43.310 --> 00:20:44.310
Magmadali.

00:20:45.870 --> 00:20:47.510
Ang totoo, ang nararamdaman ko para sa iyo, Shizuma...

00:20:50.180 --> 00:20:52.570
I should've learned my lesson
nung nakipaghiwalay sa akin si Yuka.

00:20:53.560 --> 00:20:55.380
Hindi naman ako natututo diba?

00:20:55.470 --> 00:20:56.570
Anong tanga.

00:21:00.970 --> 00:21:01.970
Binabati kita.

00:21:02.440 --> 00:21:03.500
Nakuha mo talaga ang gusto mo.

00:21:20.090 --> 00:21:21.090
alam mo,

00:21:21.970 --> 00:21:22.970
Nakita kong ginawa mo ito dati.

00:21:24.580 --> 00:21:26.050
Kung patuloy kang humahatak ng mga stunt tulad nito,

00:21:26.340 --> 00:21:27.910
hinding hindi mo makukuha ang puso ng sinuman.

00:21:29.470 --> 00:21:30.760
Mag-iisa ka habang buhay.

00:21:32.960 --> 00:21:35.230
Hindi ko naintindihan ang ibig mong sabihin noon.

00:21:36.950 --> 00:21:38.150
Pero ngayon...

00:21:39.460 --> 00:21:40.970
Nakikita ko talaga ang ibig mong sabihin.

00:22:30.460 --> 00:22:31.700
(Next Episode)
Sorry kung pinaghintay kita.

00:22:33.670 --> 00:22:34.670
Bakit?

00:22:35.070 --> 00:22:38.950
Ang Minato na kasama ni Shizuma...
kasinungalingan ba talaga ang lahat ng iyon?

00:22:39.630 --> 00:22:40.830
Wala na akong pakialam.

00:22:41.320 --> 00:22:42.550
Gusto kong hawakan mo ako.

00:22:43.540 --> 00:22:44.540
Minato.

